# quoted-string-escape-only

## Input

```
a "\n\t\\"

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..11
  ENTRY@0..11
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    QUOTED_STRING@2..10
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@2..3 "\""
      STRING@3..9 "\\n\\t\\\\"
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@9..10 "\""
    NEWLINE@10..11 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            value: QuotedString {
                open_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@2..3 "\"",
                string: STRING@3..9 "\\n\\t\\\\",
                close_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@2..3 "\"",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

